OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The father of a seven-year-old girl    
OL,6, whose hair was cut by a teacher without
OL,7, parental permission is suing the school
OL,8, district and two staff members for $1m.
OL,10,FJimmy Hoffmeyer's lawsuit says the     
OL,11,Fconstitutional rights of his mixed-race
OL,12,Fdaughter have been violated.           
OL,14,FHe has pulled his daughter out of the  
OL,15,Fschool.                                
OL,17,FAn investigation by the school district
OL,18,Fconcluded in July that while the       
OL,19,Fteacher had broken school policy she   
OL,20,Fhad not acted with racial bias.        
